column3:
These datasets contain a set of news articles in English, French and Spanish extracted from Medisys (i.e. advanced search) according the following criteria:
(1) Keywords (at least): COVID-19, ncov2019, cov2019, coronavirus;
(2) Keywords (all words): masque (French), mask (English), máscara (Spanish)
(3) Periods: March 2020, May 2020, July 2020;
(4) Countries: UK (English), Spain (Spanish), France (French).
